          <h3 class="subheading">Extension Patterns</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                <li><strong>Registry Pattern:</strong> Components registered in <span class="code">__init__.py</span></li>
                <li><strong>Factory Pattern:</strong> <span class="code">get_*()</span> functions for instantiation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                <li><strong>Strategy Pattern:</strong> Components swappable at runtime</li>
                <li><strong>Error Handling:</strong> <span class="code">ValueError</span> for invalid names</li>
              </ul>
